detail.Title: RX-78 Gundam 1st Launch & Fight (1979 VS GQuuuuuuX Comparison)[Amuro Char ガンダム ジークアクス アムロ シャア 出撃 比較]
detail.Description:
EP2 of GQuuuuuuX (2025) re-enacts scenes from EP1 of Mobile Suit Gundam (1979) where the RX-78-2 Gundam first launched. The main differences is that Char Aznable (シャア・アズナブル) is the one piloting it instead of Amuro Ray (アムロ・レイ) & he fights a Guncannon while Amuro fought Zaku IIs.
